<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Agent Application Approved</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f4f4f4; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
        .container { width: 100%; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background-color: #ffffff; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); }
        .header { text-align: center; padding-bottom: 20px; border-bottom: 1px solid #eeeeee; }
        .header h1 { color: #333333; }
        .content { padding: 20px 0; }
        .content p { font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5; color: #555555; }
        .button-container { text-align: center; padding: 20px 0; }
        .button { background-color: #28a745; color: #ffffff; padding: 10px 20px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; font-size: 16px; }
        .footer { text-align: center; padding-top: 20px; border-top: 1px solid #eeeeee; color: #aaaaaa; font-size: 12px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Congratulations, {{name}}!</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>We are thrilled to inform you that your agent application (ID: <strong>{{applicationId}}</strong>) has been <strong>approved</strong>!</p>
            <p>Welcome to the Betahouse team. We are excited to have you on board.</p>
            <p>You can now log in to your account and start managing your properties.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="button-container">
            <a href="{{loginLink}}" class="button">Go to Dashboard</a>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; {{year}} Betahouse. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
